videos.headline: Mizzou's Holmes intercepts Fromm
videos.description: Jake Fromm's pass is intercepted by Missouri's Christian Holmes.

videos.headline: Campbell puts Georgia on the board with fumble return
videos.description: Tyson Campbell forces a fumble and returns it 68 yards for a Georgia touchdown.

videos.headline: Missouri's Rountree refuses to go down on 7-yard TD run
videos.description: Larry Rountree III powers through the Georgia defense to put Missouri on the board in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Lock's pass picked off by Georgia
videos.description: Drew Lock's pass attempt is  intercepted by Georgia's Tae Crowder, who takes it deep into Missouri territory.

videos.headline: Georgia takes blocked punt to the house
videos.description: Eric Stokes blocks a Missouri punt and takes it himself for an 8-yard Georgia touchdown.

videos.headline: Smart fuming before end of 1st half
videos.description: Georgia coach Kirby Smart expresses his frustration after Missouri calls a timeout before a fourth down.

videos.headline: Fromm finds Ridley for 33-yard TD
videos.description: Riley Ridley leaps to catch Jake Fromm's pass on the sideline for a 33-yard Georgia touchdown.

videos.headline: Smart fired up again on sideline
videos.description: Kirby Smart disagrees with a roughing the passer call on Jonathan Ledbetter and does not hold back his anger.

videos.headline: Missouri RB Crockett scores 5-yard TD
videos.description: Missouri's Damarea Crockett plows through a Georgia defender to find the end zone from five yards out.

videos.headline: Holloman takes Fromm pass 61 yards to the end zone
videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Jeremiah Holloman, who stays inbounds and outraces Missouri defenders for a 61-yard score.

videos.headline: Badie scores short TD for Missouri
videos.description: MIssouri's Tyler Badie runs three yards to the end zone to cut into Georgia's lead.

videos.headline: Fromm hits Hardman in stride for 54-yard TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Mecole Hardman wide open down the middle for a 54-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Georgia takes care of business on the road against Mizzou
videos.description: Jake Fromm throws for three touchdowns in Georgia's 43-29 win over Missouri.
